Package il.org.spartan.utils

Class Range

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.org.spartan.utils.Range
  • public class Range
extends java.lang.Object
    An immutable integral range, representing all integers between from, up to, but not including, to, i.e., 
     from, from+1, ..., to-1
    Since:
    2012
    Author:
    Boris van Sosin
